1. *Broda* je skliznula sa dana. (The ship slid off the dock.)
2. Udaljenost između dve *brode* je bila veoma velika. (The distance between the two ships was very large.) 
3. On je isplovio u svoju *brodu*. (He sailed away in his ship.)
4. *Brodom* je počeo da se bavi u ranoj mladosti. (He started dealing with ships in his early youth.)
5. Ušla je na *brodu*, ali je brzo izišla. (She entered the ship, but quickly left.)
6. *Broda* je izgledalo kao da je bilo u ratu. (The ship looked as if it had been in a war.)